
1. Energy Information Administration live API data fetched

2. Meteo (weather details) live API data fetched

3. EIA's data was received by EIA in the (UTC timezone format)

4. Cleaned EIA data and converted them into EST timezone format

5. EIA data was cleaned and converted into (EST) timezone
- The EIA data covers 2025-09-15 05:00 to 2025-11-06 19:00 (EST).

6. datasets of EIA and Meteo were merged and preprocessed

7. The merged dataset was scaled and checked for missing values and N/A values

